eir first world title\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"three previous silver or bronze medals\", \"from\": 741, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest couple\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 810}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following a Stars on Ice tour last spring, they decided to continue competing for at least one more season.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Stars\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"Ice tour\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"at least one more season\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It turned out to be their best yet.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chock and Bates won all five of their competitions, including their fifth U.S. title.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0037371634618294e-39, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chock\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"their competitions\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"their fifth U.S. title\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They went into this week with the world's best total score this season by 2.6 points over Gilles and Poirier.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8278237771037326e-54, \"text\": \"Poirier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this week\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best total score\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"2.6 points\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"Gilles\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That made them the clear favorites at worlds, but not overwhelming ones.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"worlds\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1212}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They won the rhythm dance with the world's top score this season.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rhythm dance\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's top score\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gilles and Poirier outscored them by 1.05 points in the free dance, but it wasn't enough to make up their deficit from Friday.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8278237771037326e-54, \"text\": \"Poirier\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_Poirier\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gilles\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"1.05 points\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1356}, {\"ngram\": \"the free dance\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"their deficit\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chock and Bates plan to get married in June.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0037371634618294e-39, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chock\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have not announced whether they will compete next season.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a lot to celebrate coming up and a lot to evaluate before we jump into another season, because it certainly does take a lot of work and a lot of our heart and a lot of things put on hold,\\\" Chock said.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1559}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"another season\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"our heart\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1740}, {\"ngram\": \"Chock\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not out of the realm of possibility, but, also, we are not going to get ahead of ourselves.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the realm\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"possibility\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are going to re-evaluate and see how we feel at the end of the season and after our wedding.\\\"\", \"from\": 1854, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"our wedding\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If they do continue, they can bid next January to tie the record of six U.S. ice dance titles held by their former training partners, the retired Meryl Davis and Charlie White.\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meryl_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Meryl Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meryl_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Meryl_Davis\"}, {\"begin\": 2114, \"end\": 2127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_P._White\", \"score\": 0.9925999658030599, \"rank\": 0.007331148311726644, \"text\": \"Charlie White\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_P._White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_P._White\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"six U.S. ice dance titles\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2045}, {\"ngram\": \"their former training partners\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are now tied with Davis and White at two world titles.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.9998002150367883, \"rank\": 0.00013506867196677732, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Davis\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"two world titles\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No other U.S. ice dancers have won a world championship, though at least one U.S. couple won a medal at 17 of the last 19 worlds.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No other U.S. ice dancers\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2216}, {\"ngram\": \"a world championship\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"at least one U.S. couple\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 19 worlds\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The run began with Tanith Belbin and Ben Agosto taking silver at the 2005 World Championships, the first of their four medals.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2341, \"end\": 2354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanith_Belbin_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tanith Belbin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanith_Belbin_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanith_Belbin_White\"}, {\"begin\": 2359, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Agosto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Agosto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Agosto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Agosto\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The run\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2005 World Championships\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"their four medals\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That year, a 12-year-old Chock was sparked to start ice dance after watching Belbin and Agosto.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0507955355509733e-65, \"text\": \"Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ice dance\", \"from